Package org.apache.hive.hplsql

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HplsqlListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by HplsqlParser.
    HplsqlVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by HplsqlParser.
